TzHaar-Hur-Zal is the owner and operator of his shop, TzHaar-Hur-Zal's Equipment Store. Players are able to purchase various pieces of obsidian equipment as well as obsidian armour here in exchange for tokkul.

Stock[edit | edit source]

Items are only bought and sold here using Tokkul.
